   - Typography variant="h4" for page heading "Products"
   - Grid container spacing={4}
   - Map over products, each in Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}

3. Product cards:
   - Card component for each product
   - CardMedia (placeholder image area with gray background)
   - CardContent with product name (h5), price, description
   - CardActions with "View Details" and "Add to Cart" buttons
   - "View Details" links to /products/{id}

